    Pheniox coughed as she turned to look at Marine. He was more damaged then 
she, but he was the one carrying Jackle. When the ship crashed, alot of the 
crew was destroyed on impact. They were the only survivours.
    "Come on...I think were in range now to contact Commander Hell Beast. 
Lets try." She ordered, making herslef the unofficial leader of the threesome.
    Marine dropped Jackle. He was the biggest of the three. Also the 
strongest. The turtle bot picked up and communicator and turned it on. 
"Commander Hell Beast, this is Lt. Marine of Predacon Black Opp's. We are 24 
kilometers away from your position to the west, and badly damaged. Please 
send an escourt to pick us up."
    Pheniox nodded and plopped down in the snow. He would get the message, 
and they would be rescued.

    Hell Beast couldnt have been more surprized. He ordered Aquarious to take 
a shuttle with a CR chamber to thier location. His original team was all 
here...he felt so much more the Predacon Commander of the past.
